<p>Finally, thanks to <a href="http://swmansion.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Software Mansion</a> for powering this library with <code>Reanimated</code> &amp; <code>Gesture Handler</code>.</p>]]></content:encoded>
